headline: Three Reasons to Avoid SHW and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Sherwin-Williams’s 13% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 6.7%, and its stock price has climbed to $335.99 per share. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
